I"	<p>DDL(Data Definition Language): 데이터베이스나 테이블 등을 생성, 삭제하거나 그 구조를 변경하기 위한 명령어</p>

<p>Ex) CREATE, ALTER, DROP</p>

<h2 id="01-데이터베이스-생성-create">01 데이터베이스 생성 (CREATE)</h2>

<div class="language-sql highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">CREATE</span> <span class="k">DATABASE</span> <span class="err">데이터베이스이름</span><span class="p">;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="02-데이터베이스-선택-use">02 데이터베이스 선택 (USE)</h2>

<div class="language-sql highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">USE</span> <span class="err">데이터베이스이름</span><span class="p">;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="03-테이블-생성-create">03 테이블 생성 (CREATE)</h2>

<div class="language-sql highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">CREATE</span> <span class="k">TABLE</span> <span class="err">테이블이름</span>
<span class="p">(</span>
    <span class="err">필드이름</span><span class="mi">1</span> <span class="err">필드타입</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span>
    <span class="err">필드이름</span><span class="mi">2</span> <span class="err">필드타입</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span>
    <span class="p">...</span>
<span class="p">);</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Example</p>

    <div class="language-sql highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">CREATE</span> <span class="k">TABLE</span> <span class="n">Test</span>
<span class="p">(</span>
    <span class="n">ID</span> <span class="nb">INT</span><span class="p">,</span>
    <span class="n">Name</span> <span class="nb">VARCHAR</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">30</span><span class="p">),</span>
    <span class="n">ReserveDate</span> <span class="nb">DATE</span><span class="p">,</span>
    <span class="n">RoomNum</span> <span class="nb">INT</span>
<span class="p">);</span>
  
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ul>

